 (the two tints unevenly distributed), short hair dyed amother-in-law ginger, brown eyes even madder than mine, very thin lips, afat Russian nose, and three or four hairs on her chin. Before the youngreader heads for Lesbos, I wish to say that as far as I could discover (andI am a peerless spy) there was nothing sexual in her ludicrous and unlimitedaffection for my wife. I had not yet acquired the white Desert Lynx thatAnnette did not live to see, so it was Ninella who took her shopping in adila